otopic spectacles: enacted and imperfect utopias that constitute the desires, imaginings and Otherness of its society. The chapters that follow consider the different scenarios through which success was realised at the College.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Mrz 2024) 0aCommunity developmentzIndiazRajasthan. 0aElectronic books. 0aNon-governmental organizationszIndiazRajasthan. 0aNon-governmental organizationszIndia. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Anthropology / General.2bisacsh  aBarefoot College.  aBunker Roy.  aDevelopment.  aHeterotopia.  aNGO.  aSolar.  aSpectacle.1 aAllen, Stewart, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertManchester University Press 2018 eBook-Packagez978311128277040uhttps://doi.org/10.7765/978152612754940uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781526127549423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781526127549/original  a978-3-11-128277-0  Manchester University Press 2018 eBook-Packageb2018  aGBV-deGruyter-alles